Substrate 0.2.0
===

Substrate is a GUI tool which makes it easy to build text processing
pipelines.

With its ability to display intermediate results from the middle of your
pipeline, it's easy to spot which part of your pipelines don't behave as they
should.

How to use Substrate
---
Use the top pane to edit the current input for your script.
You can add alternate inputs using Project/Add Input.

Use the bottom pane to edit your script.
You can debug your script by pressing F5, which will run the script up to and
including the current line.
